00:19:40,813 --> 00:19:42,614
And not to get too weird about it,

357
00:19:42,614 --> 00:19:44,615
but he kind of starts to come to this conclusion

358
00:19:44,615 --> 00:19:47,197
that these properties are more fundamental

359
00:19:47,197 --> 00:19:51,680
than the universe itself, because no universe can exist

360
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,301
that doesn't have these properties.

